text: Eugen Radu (2018) Eugen Radu (born 16 April 1978)other sources report his date of birth as 10 April 1978 is a Romanian luger who has competed since 1994. He was born in Tulcea. Competing in two Winter Olympics, he earned his best finish of 15th in the men's doubles event both in 2002 and 2006. Radu's best finish at the FIL World Luge Championships was 14th in the men's doubles event at Nagano in 2004. ==Notes== ==References== * 2002 luge men's singles results (todor66.com) * 2002 luge men's doubles results (todor66.com) * 2006 luge men's doubles results (todor66.com) == External links == * * * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of Romania Category:Lugers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Lugers at the 2006 Winter Olympics
